summary: Imagine: Being The Doctors Daughter and, going with River your mother to the library where you meet the tenth incarnation of...
body:
Imagine: Being The Doctors Daughter and, going with River your mother to the library where you meet the tenth incarnation of your father.

The Doctor stared down at the device that was once his sonic screwdriver, it looked different, it was modified by your father in the future. The Doctor raised his eyebrow and shook his head.


“So, some time in the future, I just give you my screwdriver?” The Doctor asked.


“Yep.” You smiled.
